  <para style="toc2">Habakuk</para>
  <para style="toc3">Hab</para>
  <para style="mt1">Habakuk</para>
  <para style="mt4">(Habakuk bụ onye dere ya nʼafọ 626 tupu a mụọ Kraịst)</para>
  <para style="imt">Ihe dị nʼime ya</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ihe dị nʼime ya:</para>
  <para style="im">Habakuk buru amụma ya nʼala Juda tupu ndị Babilọn adọta ndị bi nʼime ya nʼagha. Nʼoge a, e mere ka ọ hụ ụdị ịla nʼiyi na-aga ịbịakwasị ndị ya. Nʼihi ya, Habakuk bidoro ịjụ ụzọ ajụjụ abụọ. Nke mbụ, ọ chọrọ ịmata ihe mere Chineke ji gba nkịtị mgbe ihe ọjọọ na-aba ụba nʼala Juda. Nke abụọ, ọ chọrọ ịghọta ihe mere Chineke ji kpebie iji mba a maara dịka ndị mmehie mere ngwa ọrụ ya, ịta ndị nke ya ahụhụ. Chineke zara Habakuk ajụjụ abụọ ndị a. Ma o mere karịa nke a, o mere ka Habakuk hụ ya anya. Anya Habakuk hụrụ Chineke gbakwara Habakuk ume iguzosi ike.</para>
  <para style="iot">Usoro e si dee ya:</para>
  <para style="io1">Mmehie na ahụhụ so ya <char style="ior"><ref loc="HAB 1:1-11">1:1-11</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Chineke na ndị Babilọn <char style="ior"><ref loc="HAB 1:12-2:20">1:12–2:20</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Abụ mmeri nke Habakuk <char style="ior"><ref loc="HAB 3">3</ref></char></para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="HAB 1"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HAB 1:1"/>Nke a bụ ozi Habakuk onye amụma natara.<verse eid="HAB 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Mkpesa Habakuk</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="HAB 1:2"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, ruo ole mgbe ka m ga-anọgide na-eti mkpu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:2">ma ị dịghị ege ntị?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:2">Ruo ole mgbe ka m ga na-etiku gị na-asị, “Ihe ike, ihe ike!”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:2">ma ị dịghị azọpụta?<verse eid="HAB 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="HAB 1:3"/>Nʼihi gịnị ka i ji eme m ka m na-ahụ ihe ọjọọ?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:3">Gịnị mere i ji anagide mmegbu?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:3">Mbibi na ihe ike dị nʼihu m,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:3">na ịlụ ọgụ, na esemokwu jupụtakwara ebe niile.<verse eid="HAB 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="HAB 1:4"/>Nʼihi ya, iwu na-ada mba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:4">ikpe ziri ezi adịghị agakwa nʼihu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:4">Ndị ajọ mmadụ na-agba ndị ezi omume gburugburu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:4">nke mere ka ikpe ziri ezi ghọọ ihe gbagọrọ agbagọ.<verse eid="HAB 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ọsịsa <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="HAB 1:5"/>“Legide mba niile anya, ka i hụ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:5">Lee, ka o ju gị anya nke ukwuu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:5">Nʼihi na agaje m ime ihe nʼụbọchị ndụ unu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:5">nke unu na-agaghị ekwenye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:5">ọ bụladị ma akọọrọ unu ya.<verse eid="HAB 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HAB 1:6"/>Nʼihi na lee, agaje m ime ka ndị Kaldịa bilie,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:6">bụ mba ahụ na-adịghị eme ebere, na ndị na-eme ngwangwa.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:6">Ha bụ ndị na-ebu agha na-ejegharị na mba niile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:6">ndị na-esite nʼaka ike na-enweta ebe obibi nke na-abụghị nke ha.<verse eid="HAB 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HAB 1:7"/>Ha bụ mba a na-atụ ụjọ, na ndị dịkwa egwu.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:7">Ha bụ iwu nye onwe ha, ihe ha tụpụtara ka ha na-eme.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:7">Ọ bụ onwe ha ka ha na-ebuli elu.<verse eid="HAB 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="HAB 1:8"/>Ịnyịnya ha nwere ụkwụ nkọ karịa agụ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:8">Ha na-akpa ike karịa nkịta ọhịa nke na-ejegharị nʼanyasị.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:8">Ndị ịnyịnya agha ha na-awụ ọsọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:8">ndị ha na-agba ịnyịnya na-esitekwa ebe dị anya na-abịa.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:8">Dịka ugo nke na-efedata i buru nri ọ ga-eri.<verse eid="HAB 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="HAB 1:9"/>Ha niile na-abịa ime ihe ike.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:9">Ha ji ọsọ na-abịa dịka oke ifufe nke ọzara.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:9">Ha na-abịa ịchịkọta ndị a dọtara nʼagha dịka ha bụ uzuzu.<verse eid="HAB 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="HAB 1:10"/>Ha na-akwa ndị eze emo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:10">jirikwa ndịisi ọchịchị na-eme ihe ọchị.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:10">Ha na-achị ebe niile e wusiri ike ọchị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:10">na-ekpokọtakwa aja nʼazụ mgbidi niile ịlụta ha nʼagha.<verse eid="HAB 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HAB 1:11"/>Mgbe ahụ, ha na-esi nʼebe ahụ gabiga dịka ifufe, na-agabigakwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:11">ndị mehierenụ, bụrụkwa ndị ikpe mara, ndị ike ha bụ chi ha.”<verse eid="HAB 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Mkpesa Habakuk nke ugboro abụọ</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="HAB 1:12"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, Ọ bụ na ị dịghị site mgbe niile ebighị ebi?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:12">Chineke m, na Onye Nsọ m, Ị gaghị anwụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:12">Gị, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, họpụtara ha maka ikpe ikpe.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:12">Gị, oke nkume m, emeela ka ha bụrụ ndị ga-enweta ahụhụ.<verse eid="HAB 1:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="HAB 1:13"/>Ma anya gị dị ọcha nke ukwuu, na ọ dịghị elekwasị ajọ ihe anya;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:13">ị naghị anabatakwa mmegbu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:13">Ma gịnị mere i ji gba ndị aghụghọ nkịtị?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:13">Gịnị mere i ji gba nkịtị mgbe ndị ajọ omume na-eloda</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:13">ndị bụ ndị ezi omume karịa ha?<verse eid="HAB 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="HAB 1:14"/>I meela ndị mmadụ ka ha dịrị ka azụ nke osimiri,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:14">e, dịka anụ na-akpụ akpụ nke oke osimiri, nke na-enweghị onye na-achị ha.<verse eid="HAB 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="HAB 1:15"/>Onye iro nke ajọ omume juru obi, na-eji nko ya na-egbu ha.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:15">Ọ na-ejikwa nko ụgbụ ya na-ejide ha.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:15">Ọ na-achịkọta ha nʼụgbụ ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:15">si otu a na-aṅụrị ọṅụ, ma na-etegharịkwa egwu ọṅụ.<verse eid="HAB 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="HAB 1:16"/>Nʼihi nke a, ọ na-achụ aja</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:16">na-esurekwa ihe nsure ọkụ na-esi isi ụtọ nye ụgbụ ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 1:16">nʼihi na ọ bụ ụgbụ ya na-eme ka ọ na-ebi ezi ndụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:16">na-erikwa nri kachasị mma<verse eid="HAB 1:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="HAB 1:17"/>Ọ ga-aga nʼihu mgbe niile na-awụpụ ihe o ji ụgbụ ya gbute</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 1:17">na-ala mba niile nʼiyi, dịka o si masị ya, na-egosighị obi ebere ọbụla?<verse eid="HAB 1:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="HAB 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="HAB 2"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HAB 2:1"/>Aga m arịgoro nʼelu ebe nche m,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:1">guzo onwe m nʼebe nchekwa ahụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:1">Aga m echerekwa ịhụ ihe ọ ga-agwa m,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:1">na ihe m ga-asa, banyere mkpesa ndị a.<verse eid="HAB 2:1"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ọsịsa <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="HAB 2:2"/>Mgbe ahụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara m sị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:2">“Dee ọhụ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ya bụ, ọsịsa</char></note> ahụ nʼelu mbadamba nkume e ji ede ihe.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:2">Depụta ya nke ọma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:2">ka onye na-agba ọsọ nwee ike ịgụ ya.<verse eid="HAB 2:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="HAB 2:3"/>Nʼihi na e nwere ọhụ nke ga-adị ruo oge a kara aka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:3">ọ na-ekwu banyere oge ọgwụgwụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:3">Ọ gaghị abụkwa ụgha.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:3">Ọ bụrụ na ọ dịka mmezu ya adịghị abịaru ọsịịsọ, chere mmezu ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:3">nʼihi na ọ ga-emesịa mezuo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:3">ọ gaghị anọ tee aka.<verse eid="HAB 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="HAB 2:4"/>“Lee, onye iro na-afụli onwe ya elu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:4">ọchịchọ ya ezikwaghị ezi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:4">ma onye ezi omume ga-esite nʼokwukwe<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">ikwesi ntụkwasị obi</char></note> ya dị ndụ.<verse eid="HAB 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="HAB 2:5"/>Nʼezie, mmanya<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nʼakwụkwọ ụfọdụ ihe ị ga-ahụ bụ akụnụba.</char></note> na-eduhie ya ụzọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:5">onye jupụtara na nganga, na-adịghị enwe ezumike.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:5">Ebe ọ bụ na o nwere anya ukwu dịka ala mmụọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:5">ọ gaghị enwekwa afọ ojuju dịka ọnwụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:5">Nʼihi na ọ na-achịkọta mba niile nye onwe ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:5">ọ na-adọtakwa ọtụtụ ndị mmadụ nʼagha.<verse eid="HAB 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HAB 2:6"/>“Ndị a niile ha agaghị eji ịkwa emo na nkọcha sị ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:6">“ ‘Ahụhụ dịrị onye ahụ na-atụkọta ihe e zutere nʼohi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:6">ruo ole mgbe ka ị ga-anọ na-eme onwe gị ọgaranya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:6">site nʼịnara ndị mmadụ ụgwọ nʼike?’<verse eid="HAB 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HAB 2:7"/>Ọ bụ na ndị i ji ụgwọ agaghị abịakwasị gị na mberede?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:7">Ọ bụ na ha agaghị eteta nʼụra, mee gị ka ị maa jijiji?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:7">Mgbe ahụ ka ha ga-eji gị mee ihe ha chọrọ.<verse eid="HAB 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="HAB 2:8"/>Nʼihi na ị kwakọtala akụ nke ọtụtụ mba dị iche iche,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:8">ndị ahụ fọdụrụ ga-abịakwa kwakọrọ ihe niile i nwere.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:8">Nʼihi na ị wụsịala ọbara ndị mmadụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:8">i bibiela ọtụtụ ala na obodo na ndị niile bi nʼime ha.<verse eid="HAB 2:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="HAB 2:9"/>“Ahụhụ na-adịrị onye ahụ na-ewu ụlọ ya site nʼuru ọjọọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:9">nke na-ewukwasị akwụ ya nʼebe dị elu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:9">nʼihi ịgbanarị mbibi nke ga-abịa.<verse eid="HAB 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="HAB 2:10"/>I sitela nʼizuzu ọjọọ gị mee ka mbibi bịakwasị ọtụtụ mmadụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:10">sị otu a tufuo ndụ gị, ma wetakwara ezinaụlọ gị ihere.<verse eid="HAB 2:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HAB 2:11"/>Ọ bụladị nkume ahụ e ji wuo mgbidi ga-eti mkpu megide gị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:11">Osisi e ji doo elu ụlọ ga-etikwa mkpu akwa za nkume ndị ahụ.<verse eid="HAB 2:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="HAB 2:12"/>“Ahụhụ dịrị onye ahụ na-eji ọbara ewu obodo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:12">nke na-ejikwa ajọ omume eme ka obodo ahụ guzosie ike.<verse eid="HAB 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="HAB 2:13"/>Ọ bụ na ọ bụghị uche <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, Onye pụrụ ime ihe niile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:13">na ndọgbu nʼọrụ niile nke mmadụ bụ na nkịtị, ihe e ji afụnwu ọkụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:13">na oke ọrụ niile nke mba dị iche iche bụ ihe lara nʼiyi?<verse eid="HAB 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="HAB 2:14"/>Nʼihi na ụwa niile ga-ejupụta na ihe ọmụma nke ebube <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:14">dịka mmiri si ekpuchi oke osimiri.<verse eid="HAB 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="HAB 2:15"/>“Ahụhụ dịrị onye ahụ na-enye onye agbataobi ya mmanya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:15">nke na-anọgide na-agbanyere ya mmanya tutu ruo mgbe mmanya bidoro igbu ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:15">ka o si otu a hụ ọtọ ya anya.<verse eid="HAB 2:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="HAB 2:16"/>Ihere ga-anọchi otuto na nsọpụrụ i nwere.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:16">Ṅụọ ka ị bụrụ onye mmanya na-egbu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:16">Nʼihi na iko dị nʼaka nri <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> na-abịakwute gị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:16">Ihere ga-anọchikwa anya otuto gị.<verse eid="HAB 2:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="HAB 2:17"/>Ihe ike ahụ i mere Lebanọn ga-abịakwasịkwa gị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:17">Mbibi i bibiri anụmanụ dị iche iche ga-emekwa ka egwu ju gị obi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:17">Nʼihi na ị wụsịala ọbara ọtụtụ mmadụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:17">bibie ala na obodo dị iche iche, bibiekwa ndị niile bi nʼime ha.<verse eid="HAB 2:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="HAB 2:18"/>“Gịnị bụ uru arụsị bara ebe ọ bụ aka mmadụ kpụrụ ya?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:18">Kedụ uru igwe a kpụrụ akpụ bara, bụ nke na-ekwu okwu ụgha?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:18">Nʼihi na onye na-atụkwasị ha obi na-atụkwasị obi ya nʼihe ahụ aka ya rụpụtara,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:18">nʼihi na ọ bụ arụsị na-enweghị ike ikwu okwu ka o mere.<verse eid="HAB 2:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="HAB 2:19"/>Ahụhụ dịrị onye ahụ na-agwa osisi okwu sị, ‘Dịrị ndụ.’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:19">Ma ọ bụ nkume nke na-apụghị ikwu okwu, ‘Teta nʼụra.’</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 2:19">O nwere ike izi mmadụ ihe?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:19">Lee, ọ bụ ihe eji ọlaọcha na ọlaedo machie,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:19">ma ọ dịghị nkuume ọbụla dị nʼime ya.”<verse eid="HAB 2:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="HAB 2:20"/>Ma <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nọ nʼime ụlọnsọ ukwu ya.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 2:20">Ya mere, ka ụwa niile dere duu nʼihu ya.<verse eid="HAB 2:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HAB 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="HAB 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Ekpere Habakuk</para>
  <para style="d">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HAB 3:1"/>Nke a bụ ekpere Habakuk onye amụma kpere. Ọ dị nʼusoro <char style="it">Shiginot.</char> Nke a bụ ihe o kwuru.<verse eid="HAB 3:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="HAB 3:2"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> anụla m ihe niile e kwuru banyere ude gị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:2">Ịdị ukwuu nke ọrụ gị niile na-emekwa ka m dere duu nʼegwu nʼihu gị, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:2">Mekwaa ya ọzọ nʼoge nke anyị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:2">mekwaa ka anụ akụkọ ya nʼọgbọ anyị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:2">Nʼoke iwe gị chetakwa ebere.<verse eid="HAB 3:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="HAB 3:3"/>Chineke si na Teman bịa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:3">Onye Nsọ ahụ sikwa nʼugwu Paran. <char style="qs">Sela</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:3">Ebube ya na-ekpuchi eluigwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:3">otuto ya jupụtakwara nʼụwa.<verse eid="HAB 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="HAB 3:4"/>Ịma mma ya na-achapụta dịka ihe anyanwụ ụtụtụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:4">ihe na-enwupụta site nʼaka ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:4">ọ bụkwa nʼebe ahụ ka e zoro ike ya.<verse eid="HAB 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="HAB 3:5"/>Nʼihu ya ka ajọ ọrịa na-efe efe na-aga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:5">oke mbibi na-esokwa ya nʼazụ.<verse eid="HAB 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HAB 3:6"/>O guzoro ọtọ yọgharịa ụwa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:6">o lere anya, mee ka mba niile maa jijiji.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:6">Ugwu ukwu ochie ahụ niile dara,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:6">ugwu nta ochie ndị ahụ dakwara.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:6">Nʼihi na ụzọ ya ga-adịgide ruo mgbe niile ebighị ebi.<verse eid="HAB 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HAB 3:7"/>Ahụrụ m ụlọ ikwu nke Kushan ka ha nọ ọnọdụ ụbọchị ọjọọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:7">na ebe obibi ndị Midia ka ha nọ na oke ahụ ụfụ.<verse eid="HAB 3:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="HAB 3:8"/>Ọ bụ osimiri, ka gị bụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> were iwe megide?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:8">Ọnụma gị, ọ dị ukwuu megide iyi niile?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:8">Oke iwe gị ọ bụ megide oke osimiri</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:8">mgbe ị nọkwasịrị nʼelu ịnyịnya gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:8">nakwa nʼelu ụgbọ ịnyịnya ị wetara ndị nke gị mmeri?<verse eid="HAB 3:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="HAB 3:9"/>I kpughepụrụ ụta gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:9">kpọọ oku ka a chịtara gị ọtụtụ àkụ. <char style="qs">Sela</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:9">I ji osimiri dị iche iche kewaa ụwa.<verse eid="HAB 3:9"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="HAB 3:10"/>Mgbe ugwu niile hụrụ gị ha nyagharịrị onwe ha nʼihi ihe mgbu bịakwasịrị ha.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:10">Oke mmiri ozuzo gabigakwara.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:10">Ogbu mmiri mere ka olu ya daa ụda,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:10">buliekwa ebili mmiri elu.<verse eid="HAB 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HAB 3:11"/>Anyanwụ na ọnwa guzokwara duu na mbara eluigwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:11">mgbe ha hụrụ ihe nke àkụ gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:11">mgbe ha hụrụ amụma nke ùbe gị gburu.<verse eid="HAB 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="HAB 3:12"/>I sitere nʼọnụma gị zọgharịa ije nʼụwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:12">sitekwa nʼiwe gị zọchaa mba dị iche iche dịka ọka.<verse eid="HAB 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="HAB 3:13"/>Ị pụtara ịzọpụta ndị gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:13">ịzọpụta onye ahụ i tere mmanụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:13">Ị zọpịara isi onyendu nke ala ajọ omume ahụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:13">gbawa ya ọtọ site nʼisi ruo nʼụkwụ.<verse eid="HAB 3:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="HAB 3:14"/>Ọ bụ ùbe ya ka i ji mawaa ya isi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:14">mgbe ndị dike nʼagha ya bịara dịka oke ifufe ịchụsa anyị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:14">mgbe ha si nʼobi ụtọ ha chee na ha na-aga iripịa ndị ogbenye e wedara nʼala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:14">bụ ndị na-ezo onwe ha.<verse eid="HAB 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="HAB 3:15"/>Ị chịrịla ịnyịnya gị zọọ ije nʼoke osimiri,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:15">kpagharịa mmiri ukwu ndị ahụ.<verse eid="HAB 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="HAB 3:16"/>Amara m jijiji nʼobi m mgbe m nụrụ ihe ndị a niile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:16">egbugbere ọnụ m abụọ kụkọtara nʼegwu,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:16">ọkpụkpụ dị m nʼahụ malitere ire ure,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:16">mee ka ụkwụ m maa jijiji.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:16">Ma aga m eji ndidi chere ụbọchị ọjọọ ahụ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:16">nke ga-abịakwasị ndị ahụ na-abịa ibuso anyị agha.<verse eid="HAB 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="HAB 3:17"/>A sịkwarị na osisi fiig amaghị ifuru,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:17">na ọ dịghị mkpụrụ dị nʼosisi vaịnị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:17">a sịkwa na mkpụrụ osisi oliv ebilata</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:17">na ala ubi niile emepụtaghị ihe oriri,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HAB 3:17">a sịkwa na ọ dịghị atụrụ dị nʼọgba anụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:17">na ọ dịkwaghị ehi nọ nʼụlọ anụmanụ,<verse eid="HAB 3:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="HAB 3:18"/>mụ onwe m ga-anọgide na-aṅụrị ọṅụ nʼime <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:18">Aga m etegharịkwa egwu ọṅụ nʼime Chineke Onye nzọpụta m.<verse eid="HAB 3:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="HAB 3:19"/>Onye kachasị ihe niile elu, bụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> bụ ike m,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:19">ọ na-eme ụkwụ m abụọ ka ha dịka nke ele.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:19 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ịdị ngwa nʼịgba ọsọ</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HAB 3:19">Ọ na-emekwa ka m zọọ ije nʼebe niile dị elu.</para>
  <para style="d" vid="HAB 3:19">Nke a dịrị onyeisi abụ, nʼụbọ akwara m dị iche iche.<verse eid="HAB 3:19"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HAB 3"/>
</usx>
